        "copyright": "Cascada Horsetail, parque nacional de Yosemite, California, EE. UU. (© Jorge Villalba/Getty Images)",
        "copyrightlink": "https://www.bing.com/search?q=Cascada+Horsetail&form=hpcapt&filters=HpDate%3a%2220260219_2300%22",
        "title": "Donde cae la luz",
