        "copyright": "Estanques de evaporación de sal en la isla de Gozo, Malta (© Marius Roman/Getty Images)",
        "copyrightlink": "https://www.bing.com/search?q=Gozo+Malta&form=hpcapt&filters=HpDate%3a%2220260204_2300%22",
