        "copyright": "Atrio abierto de ocho plantas del Ayuntamiento de Milwaukee, Wisconsin, EE. UU. (© lavin photography/Getty Images)",
        "copyrightlink": "https://www.bing.com/search?q=Milwaukee+Wisconsin+en+Estados+Unidos&form=hpcapt&filters=HpDate%3a%2220260128_2300%22",
        "title": "Una historia exagerada de Milwaukee",
