        "copyright": "Fortaleza de Gwalior, Madhya Pradesh, India (© ImagesofIndia/Shutterstock)",
        "copyrightlink": "https://www.bing.com/search?q=India&form=hpcapt&filters=HpDate%3a%2220251123_2300%22",
        "title": "Secretos tallados en piedra",
