        "copyright": "Rocas de Belogradchik, Bulgaria (© EvaL Miko/Shutterstock)",
        "copyrightlink": "https://www.bing.com/search?q=Fortaleza+Belogradchik&form=hpcapt&filters=HpDate%3a%2220251021_2200%22",
        "title": "Grabado en piedra",
