        "copyright": "Oxbow Bend en el río Snake, Parque Nacional Grand Teton, Wyoming, EE. UU. (© DanitaDelimont.com/AWL Images/SuperStock)",
        "copyrightlink": "https://www.bing.com/search?q=Parque+Nacional+Grand+Teton&form=hpcapt&filters=HpDate%3a%2220251001_2200%22",
        "title": "Salvaje por ley",
        "quiz": "/search?q=Bing+homepage+quiz&filters=WQOskey:%22HPQuiz_20251001_OxbowBend%22&FORM=HPQUIZ",
