        "copyright": "Lago Sørvágsvatn, Isla de Vágar, Islas Feroe, Reino de Dinamarca (© Anton Petrus/Getty Images)",
        "copyrightlink": "https://www.bing.com/search?q=S%C3%B8rv%C3%A1gsvatn&form=hpcapt&filters=HpDate%3a%2220250826_2200%22",
